OL,3,CWaspi campaigners to gather outside
OL,4,CRoyal Courts of Justice on Monday
OL,6,FA previous report by the Parliamentary
OL,7,Fand Health Service Ombudsman (PSHO)
OL,8,Fsuggested compensation ranging between
OL,9,F#1,000 and #2,950 could be appropriate
OL,10,Ffor each of those affected.
OL,12,FBut in December 2024, the Government
OL,13,Fsaid that, while it accepted the
OL,14,Fombudsman's finding of
OL,15,Fmaladministration and apologised for
OL,16,Fthere being a delay in writing to
OL,17,F1950s-born women, a blanket
OL,18,Fcompensation scheme, which could cost
OL,19,Ftaxpayers up to #10.5 billion, cannot
OL,20,Fbe justified.
