OL,6,FCampaigners said they have raised more
OL,7,Fthan #150,000 in recent weeks to fund
OL,8,Fa High Court challenge.
OL,10,FWaspi chair Angela Madden said: "We do
OL,11,Fnot want to be taking legal action,
OL,12,Fbut we have been forced to, due to the
OL,13,FGovernment's total denial of justice."
OL,15,FLawyers for the campaigners argue that
OL,16,Fthe Government's reasons for
OL,17,Fconcluding that people should not
OL,18,Freceive any remedy are a breach of
OL,19,Flegal principles.
