OL,6,F"However, evidence showed only one in
OL,7,Ffour people remember reading and
OL,8,Freceiving letters that they weren't
OL,9,Fexpecting and that by 2006 90% of
OL,10,F1950s-born women knew that the state
OL,11,Fpension age was changing.
OL,13,F"The Government cannot justify paying
OL,14,Ffor a #10.5 billion compensation
OL,15,Fscheme at the expense of the taxpayer."
